{"tid":898981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌驚現蝕讓成交","createTime":"2018-11-12T05:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T10:42:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"233cb233585fa27ef2e3e77e433a4e3c0e21d8b8","tid":898981,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"東涌驚現蝕讓成交，東堤灣畔一個頂層特色戶造價近4年前帳面蝕12萬元。<br />\n<br />\n美聯物業分行營業經理吳惠斌表示，屋苑2座頂層特色戶，實用面積1,159平方呎，另有440平方呎平台，業主早於4月份委託小型代理公司以1700萬獨家代理放售，每呎叫價約1.47萬元，當時仍是樓市高位，惟市，至最近市場氣氛轉變，加上獨家代理放售期完成，轉在市場上其他代理放售，更降價至1,450萬，反應依然不佳，最終剛剛再減價至1188萬元易手，累積減價512萬或30%，呎價低見10,250元。<br />\n<br />\n代理指：「個市已經直插，業主唔想再睇落去」值得留意，原業主於2015年1月以1200萬元購入單位，持貨不足4年，帳面已蝕讓12萬元。<br />\n<br />\n吳惠斌指，屋苑頂層特色戶今年錄得2宗買賣成交，成交價分別1,950萬及1,988萬元，呎價分別1.54萬及1.41萬左右水平。"},{"pid":"4c94c6b6d1a8843e0d068e2668a03ffc42c66bcb","tid":898981,"uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p8o5jz1i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp8o5jz1i&h=60079516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ez6vbp9w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fez6vbp9w&h=4ec81e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1gdkI7IUrhbTWu8cWX/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1gdkI7IUrhbTWu8cWX%2Fgiphy.gif&h=d68c158b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/nwujxzDMlKGbIyyZgN/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FnwujxzDMlKGbIyyZgN%2Fgiphy.gif&h=f54254f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/5UsaAFe0F4kwfOujd2/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F5UsaAFe0F4kwfOujd2%2Fgiphy.gif&h=f5e5ec48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjEFFtG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjEFFtG.gif&h=0cecadeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"774d8f270914b963a384853cd54d4230452a0d03","tid":898981,"uid":107927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:37:52.000Z","msg":"東涌唔計"},{"pid":"473754da0a4b8a4913dbba1599ad907c75238872","tid":898981,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:43:14.000Z","msg":"中間自住四年/租出去賺左幾多硬淡又唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢次都唔計呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cfb9aeed7b9fec0221aef0817aed45fb0997ae","tid":898981,"uid":164167,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rpMMG5G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrpMMG5G.png&h=115e07ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4337d978bcd449024c4eb2c84dceffce85f9e8d","tid":898981,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"東涌唔計<br />\n香港樓市只升不跌"},{"pid":"f8f0991371646cf713c5c7cbef3fd36131eafe27","tid":898981,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"龍心住果頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fd7b61db37c8cecbfc30d71225fdabab4d2e32","tid":898981,"uid":208227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"傻鳩先放獨家"},{"pid":"c51f1e043117fa77926060058922dcf51a9e12de","tid":898981,"uid":78304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T06:15: